Package: forestFragR
Title: Forest Fragmentation and Connectivity Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Patience", "Birungi", , "birungipatience11@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for analyzing forest fragmentation and spatial
    connectivity using raster data with the 'terra' and 'ggplot2'
    packages. Includes functions for preprocessing land cover data,
    identifying patches, computing landscape metrics, and visualizing
    patch isolation to support ecological and geospatial analysis.
